---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About | Auto-Mate AI Automation"
  description="Auto-Mate was built by Kaden to help service-based businesses eliminate the manual work that technology should handle. Based in Orem, UT."
  currentPage="/about"
>

  <!-- PAGE HERO -->
  <section style="background: var(--color-am-dark); padding: 80px 0 64px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-am-border);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="eyebrow">About Auto-Mate</div>
      <h1 class="section-heading" style="font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem); max-width: 640px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Built by someone who has seen the waste firsthand
      </h1>
      <p class="section-subheading">
        Auto-Mate exists because too many good businesses are being held back by work that technology should be doing. We fix that.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- STORY -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-am-mid);">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 72px; align-items: start;" class="story-grid">

        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">The Story</div>
          <h2 class="section-heading" style="font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.4rem); margin-bottom: 28px;">
            The problem is not your team. It is your systems.
          </h2>

          <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-am-muted); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            Most businesses at the $500K to $5M level have proven their model. They have customers, a team, and real revenue. But they hit a ceiling, because growth requires more headcount, and more headcount means more overhead, more management, and more complexity.
          </p>

          <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-am-muted); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            The real issue is that a huge portion of the daily workload, responding to leads, chasing follow-ups, moving data between systems, pulling reports, is work that a well-designed automation system can handle with zero human involvement.
          </p>

          <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-am-muted); line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 20px;">
            Auto-Mate was built to solve exactly that. We identify where your operation is leaking time and revenue, and we build the systems that stop the leak. No software platforms to learn. No complicated dashboards. Just results.
          </p>

          <p style="font-size: 1rem; color: var(--color-am-muted); line-height: 1.85;">
            Every system is built from scratch for your business. The tools you already use. The workflows you already have. We wire it all together so the repetitive work happens without anyone having to think about it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <!-- Founder card -->
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">
            <div style="
              width: 80px;
              height: 80px;
              background: var(--color-am-blue-dim);
              border: 2px solid rgba(201, 78, 40, 0.25);
              border-radius: 50%;
              display: flex;
              align-items: center;
              justify-content: center;
              margin-bottom: 20px;
              font-family: var(--font-display);
              font-size: 1.8rem;
              font-weight: 700;
              color: var(--color-am-blue);
            ">K</div>
            <h3 style="font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px;">Kaden</h3>
            <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-am-blue); font-weight: 500; margin-bottom: 16px;">Founder, Auto-Mate</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.92rem; color: var(--color-am-muted); line-height: 1.7;">
              Based in Orem, UT. Kaden builds custom workflow automation for service businesses, helping owners reclaim time and grow revenue without adding headcount. His focus is on practical systems that deliver measurable results, not theoretical AI projects.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Contact quick card -->
          <div style="background: var(--color-am-card); border: 1px solid var(--color-am-border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px;">
            <p style="font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.08em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-am-subtle); margin-bottom: 16px;">Get in touch</p>
            <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px;">
              <a href="mailto:kaden@auto-mate.business" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; color: var(--color-am-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; transition: color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='var(--color-am-text)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='var(--color-am-muted)'">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-am-blue)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/>
                </svg>
                kaden@auto-mate.business
              </a>
              <a href="tel:8014583118" style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; color: var(--color-am-muted); font-size: 0.9rem; transition: color 0.2s;" onmouseover="this.style.color='var(--color-am-text)'" onmouseout="this.style.color='var(--color-am-muted)'">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-am-blue)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12 19.79 19.79 0 0 1 1.61 3.37 2 2 0 0 1 3.59 1h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L7.91 8.54a16 16 0 0 0 5.55 5.55l.92-.92a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 21 16.92z"/>
                </svg>
                (801) 458-3118
              </a>
              <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; color: var(--color-am-muted); font-size: 0.9rem;">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-am-blue)" stroke-width="1.75" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
                </svg>
                Orem, UT
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VALUES / APPROACH -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-am-dark);">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 64px;">
        <div class="eyebrow">How We Work</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading">A few things we believe strongly</h2>
      </div>

      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 24px;">

        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">No templates. Ever.</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-am-muted); line-height: 1.75;">Generic automation is almost as bad as no automation. If it does not fit your exact workflow, your team will route around it. Everything we build is custom to your business from day one.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">You should not need to learn anything new.</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-am-muted); line-height: 1.75;">The systems we build work inside the tools you already use. Your CRM, your email platform, your scheduling software. We plug automation into your existing workflow so adoption is immediate.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">The audit is not a sales pitch.</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-am-muted); line-height: 1.75;">The 45-minute audit is a working session. We map your workflow, identify the gaps, and tell you straight what automation would and would not help. Some businesses are not ready yet. We will tell you that too.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">Outcomes, not hours.</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-am-muted); line-height: 1.75;">We do not charge by the hour. We scope a project based on the value of the problem being solved. If we build something that saves you $10,000 per month, the investment reflects that.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">We stay. We do not just build and disappear.</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-am-muted); line-height: 1.75;">Automation needs maintenance as your business evolves. We stay on as your long-term automation partner, keeping systems running and building new ones as your operation grows.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
          <h3 style="font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;">Practical AI, not buzzword AI.</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-am-muted); line-height: 1.75;">We use AI where it makes a real, measurable difference. Not because it sounds impressive. Not as a marketing angle. If the solution is simpler without it, we will build it that way and charge you accordingly.</p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-am-surface) 0%, #0F1520 100%); border-top: 1px solid var(--color-am-border); padding: 80px 0;">
    <div class="container" style="text-align: center; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <h2 style="font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.4rem); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 20px;">
        Let us figure out where your biggest opportunity is
      </h2>
      <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-am-muted); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 36px;">
        Book a free 45-minute AI audit. No pitch, no pressure. Just a real conversation about what automation could do for your specific business.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary" style="font-size: 1rem; padding: 16px 32px;">
        Book Your Free Audit
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .story-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    }
  }
</style>
